 R Kabel Limited","website":"https://www.rrkabel.com","city":"Mumbai","full_time_employees":3678,"trailing_pe":32.783043,"forward_pe":25.339556,"price_to_book":6.3538556,"book_value":206.898,"eps_trailing":40.1,"eps_forward":51.87936,"dividend_rate":8.0,"dividend_yield":0.61,"payout_ratio":0.1871,"revenue":89760530432.0,"revenue_per_share":793.741,"revenue_growth":0.423,"ebitda":6909517824.0,"ebitda_margins":0.07698,"gross_margins":0.18358,"operating_margins":0.07112,"profit_margins":0.050279997,"net_income":4513040896.0,"total_cash":269816992.0,"total_cash_per_share":2.387,"total_debt":3926219008.0,"debt_to_equity":16.78,"enterprise_value":152266031104.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":22.037,"enterprise_to_revenue":1.696,"earnings_growth":0.722,"shares_outstanding":113105505.0,"float_shares":33617473.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.70262,"held_pct_institutions":0.18112,"beta":1.345,"fifty_two_week_high":1578.2,"fifty_two_week_low":864.05,"fifty_day_average":1439.21,"two_hundred_day_avg":1364.436,"target_high_price":2200.0,"target_low_price":1530.0,"target_mean_price":1876.0,"recommendation":"none","num_analyst_opinions":11,"all_time_high":1901.95,"all_time_low":853.55,"long_business_summary":"R R Kabel Limited manufactures and sells wires and cables, and fast-moving electrical goods in India and internationally. The company offers house wires, industrial wires, low and medium voltage power cables, and special cables. It also provides low smoke zero halogen, heat resistant and flame retardant, and halogen free panel wires; fire survival, LAN and Co-X, submersible and elevator flat, home automation, airfield lighting, HT and LT power, halogen free multi and single core, steel braided, instrumentation, HV and EHV power, braided, control, DC and floating solar, halogen free, data and communication, aluminium flexible, copper flexible, battery, BMS, MODBUS, PROcess field bus, servo and drag chain, flexible single and multicore core, trirated, and auto cables; and braided straps. In addition, the company offers ceiling, table pedestal and wall, exhaust, and industrial fans; panel and down light, bulbs, and streetlights; MCB, DB, and modular switches; and water and room heaters, irons, and coolers, as well as switchgears and other appliances under the RR Signature brand name. Its products are used in residential, commercial, industrial, and infrastructure sectors. The company was formerly known as Ram Ratna Agro-Plast Limited and changed its name to R R Kabel Limited in November 2000. R R Kabel Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}